 With Christmas just days away, the Marine Corps Toys for Tots campaign is 
9,000 toys short of its goal to provide 38,000 toys to needy children in 
Ventura County. 
</P>
<P>
 Marine Staff Sgt. John Hendrix, coordinator of the effort, said the corps 
